query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('continuity',
'derivatives',
'elementary-set-theory',
'functions',
'geometry',
'inequality',
'linear-transformations',
'logic',
'modular-arithmetic',
'qgis',
'recurrence-relations',
'reference-request',
'sql-server',
'trigonometry')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('dba',
'gis',
'math',
'mathoverflow',
'salesforce')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
